Summary: This section describes the properties of the Projection class, representing its basis vectors.

Properties:
* w (Vector4): Default: Vector4(0, 0, 0, 1)
* x (Vector4): Default: Vector4(1, 0, 0, 0)
* y (Vector4): Default: Vector4(0, 1, 0, 0)
* z (Vector4): Default: Vector4(0, 0, 1, 0)
